visual.name: SankeyChart
visual.description: Sankey chart by Powerviz is a flow diagram that visualizes the proportional movement of data, resources, or processes between different categories or stages, using weighted flows to represent the magnitude of connections. The advanced Sankey Chart includes vertical and horizontal charts, adding multiple levels, highlighting and moving nodes, fill patterns, 30+ color palettes, conditional formatting, ranking, sorting, import/export, and many more.
